OL,3,CRomance scams surge leaving broken
OL,4,Chearts and empty bank accounts
OL,6,FFraudsters typically spend months
OL,7,Fgrooming their victims, building trust
OL,8,Fand emotional dependence before asking
OL,9,Ffor money.
OL,11,FOnce victims make a payment, the
OL,12,Frequests will continue to come.
OL,14,FData of TSB customers showcase victims
OL,15,Fmaking an average of 11 payments per
OL,16,Fscam and losing around #7,500 before
OL,17,Frealising they have been defrauded.
OL,19,FThe average scam relationship lasts
OL,20,Fjust over three months, with payments
OL,21,Fspread across 95 days.
