OL,6,FHowever, TSB highlighted one extreme
OL,7,Fcase in which a victim made nearly 50
OL,8,Fpayments over a period of 42 months,
OL,9,Fdespite receiving education and
OL,10,Fsecurity support.
OL,12,FFraudsters commonly rely on elaborate
OL,13,Fbackstories to explain their
OL,14,Funavailability and maintain the
OL,15,Fillusion of a relationship. In 43% of
OL,16,Fcases, scammers claimed to be living
OL,17,Fabroad.
