OL,6,FVictims aged 55`64 made up 19%, while
OL,7,Fboth over-75s and those aged 25`34
OL,8,Faccounted for 16% each.
OL,10,FSocial media played a major role in
OL,11,Fthe spread of scams, with 58% of cases
OL,12,Foriginating on these platforms.
OL,13,FFacebook was linked to the highest
OL,14,Fnumber of incidents, responsible for
OL,15,F30% of TSB's total cases. Dating apps
OL,16,Fand online dating services were also
OL,17,Fsignificant, accounting for 42% of
OL,18,Freported scams.
